        <h3>Source</h3>
                                    <div class="element-text">Emperor Meiji to President Grant on Iwakura Mission, 1871. Adopted from the official translation as reproduced in <em>The New York Times</em>, March 5, 1872.</div>
                    </div><!-- end element -->
